{"id":586123,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/06/【众人推】六月四日-不需想起-从不忘记/","date":"2018-06-04T08:37:54Z","modified":"2018-06-04T08:37:54Z","title":"【众人推】六月四日 不需想起 从不忘记","content":"<p>2018年6月4日是天安门事件29周年，推特中文圈不少推友发布图片、视频、文字表达对这一特殊时间、特殊事件的提醒、纪念，数字时代编辑选摘了部分内容整合如下：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">黑壓壓的天安門<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/tiananmen?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#tiananmen</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/June4th?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#June4th</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/zhangxiaogang?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#zhangxiaogang</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/8xwm0aQYc6\">pic.twitter.com/8xwm0aQYc6</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Han Yan (@HanYanYuen) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HanYanYuen/status/1003493909140365312?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 4, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">前两天推上收的图今天可以放出来了 #8964 <a href=\"https://t.co/NTyS5Ciwrt\">pic.twitter.com/NTyS5Ciwrt</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Seven Yu (@dofy) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/dofy/status/1003314238947856384?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">彭丽媛天安门演唱会29周年。 <a href=\"https://t.co/AQMZGSxFr1\">pic.twitter.com/AQMZGSxFr1</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 共青团流亡中央 (@ComYouthLeague) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ComYouthLeague/status/1003436305961775104?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 4, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">一九八九年學運，法官上街遊行聲援學生支持學潮，那時候的法官是有良知的，是有擔當的。 <a href=\"https://t.co/X4Cg5Ye0GF\">pic.twitter.com/X4Cg5Ye0GF</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 即管笑 (@xwh3ab) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/xwh3ab/status/1003185439140802560?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">🕯 R.I.P. to those who died on this day 29 years ago <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/tankmen2018?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#tankmen2018</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E5%9D%A6%E5%85%8B%E4%BA%BA2018?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#坦克人2018</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/glsbu9uU0i\">https://t.co/glsbu9uU0i</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/uFhUrFwUlK\">pic.twitter.com/uFhUrFwUlK</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Jian Alan Huang (@hnjhj) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hnjhj/status/1003517787774390275?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 4, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>https://twitter.com/MoeGlaze/status/1003322413277327363</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"und\" dir=\"ltr\">123 5 7  0 <a href=\"https://t.co/clWZ5pdvlX\">pic.twitter.com/clWZ5pdvlX</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; なそきん🌻 (@realNasokin) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/realNasokin/status/1003403114509037568?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"ja\" dir=\"ltr\">国会山前 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E5%9D%A6%E5%85%8B%E4%BA%BA?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#坦克人</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/TankMan2018?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#TankMan2018</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/TankMan?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#TankMan</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/3tuObs3NV0\">pic.twitter.com/3tuObs3NV0</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 周锋锁 Fengsuo Zhou (@ZhouFengSuo) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZhouFengSuo/status/1003283358636560392?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"ja\" dir=\"ltr\">平成元年の中国と平成最後の年の中国🤐 <a href=\"https://t.co/vJ4e5mX4B5\">pic.twitter.com/vJ4e5mX4B5</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; ただの主夫･まぬか@china (@manukatsunakan) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/manukatsunakan/status/1003226073276956672?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">迈克·蓬佩奥国务卿：我们记得天安门广场上无辜生命的惨痛逝去。保护人权是所有国家的基本责任。我们同国际社会一道敦促中国对29年前的事件做出公开彻底的说明。<a href=\"https://t.co/hHY11V2Egw\">https://t.co/hHY11V2Egw</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/DE9AAQFfQy\">https://t.co/DE9AAQFfQy</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 美国驻华使领馆 US MissionCN (@USA_China_Talk) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/USA_China_Talk/status/1003481811182342144?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 4, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">稍有常识的人都会看出 <a href=\"https://t.co/dJrDWqBjdP\">pic.twitter.com/dJrDWqBjdP</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 午夜游民 (@bafield) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/bafield/status/1003503844205051904?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 4, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Tianfu Square in Chengdu in May 1989. Often on this day memory focuses on Beijing and Tiananmen Square. But the protests and the bloodshed were far from confined to the capital, and in Chengdu resistance to the troops extended days beyond June 4. <a href=\"https://t.co/LqAOqFKeJ1\">https://t.co/LqAOqFKeJ1</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/gyTIwDKnuX\">pic.twitter.com/gyTIwDKnuX</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Chris Buckley 储百亮 (@ChuBailiang) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ChuBailiang/status/1003446270260797440?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 4, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">话说前些年 Noodler&#39;s 出过一款血红色墨水，取名「天安门」，吐槽吐到飞起，这几天刚好在家翻出来，六四应个景。 <a href=\"https://t.co/jytmbwIEXl\">pic.twitter.com/jytmbwIEXl</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; fivestone (@fivestone) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/fivestone/status/1003465841332011008?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 4, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">大部分互联网服务选择在这一天关闭论坛，关闭搜索，加强审查，反而是在提醒大家这一天的到来。 <a href=\"https://t.co/4V2mFI7jUP\">pic.twitter.com/4V2mFI7jUP</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 陈少举 (@chenshaoju) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/chenshaoju/status/1003461421643026432?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 4, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">人家地铁好心便民提醒，防止给大家的出行生活带来不便，怎么就违反相关法律法规了啊？本来应该互相转告的出行信息，反而转发不了了。 <a href=\"https://t.co/W0S3YO1hhj\">pic.twitter.com/W0S3YO1hhj</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 神楽坂雅詩 (@kagurazakayashi) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/kagurazakayashi/status/1003169490488573952?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">天暗如晦，暴雨待注，是要清洗这块已经污浊不堪的土地？还是要荡涤这个灵魂已经出窍的民族？近九千个日日夜夜，凡八千里山山水水，列祖列宗在上，历代历朝在前，为何神灵不再？鬼雄不哭？弃我学子于荒野，恸我母亲于长夜，故国乡关，可有青山？白云苍狗，魂归何处？归来兮，四方不可以托些，惟心永存。 <a href=\"https://t.co/pmuURCcm4v\">pic.twitter.com/pmuURCcm4v</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 荣剑 (@rongjian1957) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/rongjian1957/status/1003257724774199296?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">坦克碾人图，来个不血腥的创意内涵版本！ <a href=\"https://t.co/NEq64gnE03\">pic.twitter.com/NEq64gnE03</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 成涛漫画 cartoon &amp; comic (@taocomic) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/taocomic/status/1003526662120726528?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 4, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"und\" dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://t.co/74ic3PivaT\">pic.twitter.com/74ic3PivaT</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 乖乖＠【blog圖黨】 (@blogtd) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/blogtd/status/1003495730860908544?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 4, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"ja\" dir=\"ltr\">中国のネット規制 </p>\n<p>本日、中国のチャットアプリWeChatの红包(ラッキーマネー)機能も規制されました。</p>\n<p>红包はネットで友人にお金を送付できるという機能ですが、本日に限って、89.64元の指定金の送付ができません。</p>\n<p>中国政府は天安門事件をどれだけ警戒しているのか、お分かりでしょうか <a href=\"https://t.co/9P8L5tRjKD\">pic.twitter.com/9P8L5tRjKD</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 地蛋 (@Wl9uZ) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Wl9uZ/status/1003534342008664064?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 4, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">从来不需要想起，永远也不会忘记。 <a href=\"https://t.co/dcno5dcAbr\">pic.twitter.com/dcno5dcAbr</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 不留行影👩‍🎤 (@luanma_) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/luanma_/status/1003317529538789381?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E8%A8%80%E8%AE%BA?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#言论</a> 技术是历史的成果，但技术无法抹去历史。苍山独厚 <a href=\"https://t.co/q6WAVuN3Oa\">pic.twitter.com/q6WAVuN3Oa</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 苍山独厚 (@CangShanDuHou) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CangShanDuHou/status/1003277531317927936?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">王怡牧师：今天是“为国家祷告月”的最后一天，也是教会鼓励大家参加的“禁食祷告日”。愿更多但弟兄姊妹，在今天以禁食、默想、认罪、怜悯、祈祷，为国家族群祷告，求主赦免罪恶，也求主施行公义。求主安慰忧伤苦痛者，也求主击打良心麻木的人。 <a href=\"https://t.co/ZU2XdKByAv\">pic.twitter.com/ZU2XdKByAv</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; jasonwang365 (@jasonwang4587) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jasonwang4587/status/1003483617232908288?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 4, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,17016],"tags":[19985,34821,10210,19752]}